      "content": "it's probably just jet lag right? he's always been a bit sensitive to travel and he's pretty old. i don't want to freak him out or make him go to the hospital if he just needs a good nap and some water. do you think it's okay if we just let him sleep it off for a few hours and see if he feels better in the morning?",
